{"id":242,"date":"2025-08-29T05:17:45","date_gmt":"2025-08-28T23:47:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=242"},"modified":"2025-08-31T03:04:05","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:34:05","slug":"contact-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/contact-us\/","title":{"rendered":"Contact Us"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Bunnings-BBQ-3-min.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Bunnings-BBQ-3-min.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">How can we help you?<\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cEvery great journey begins with a simple step, and every act of service begins with a connection. At the Lions Club of Balasore, we believe that communication is the bridge that brings hearts together and turns compassion into action. Whether you wish to join our mission, support our causes, partner with us, or simply learn more, we are here to listen, guide, and walk beside you. Your words, ideas, and presence matter to us, for they hold the power to inspire change and strengthen our shared vision of service. Reach out today\u2014not just to contact us, but to become a part of a movement that touches lives and transforms communities.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"marg